'''史葛·保羅·卡臣'''（{{lang-en|'''Scott Paul Carson'''}}，{{bd|1985年|9月3日|catIdx=Carson, Scott}}），出生於[[坎布里亞郡|坎布里亞郡]][[懷特黑文|懷特黑文]]，是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[門將|門將]]，目前由[[英冠|英冠]]俱樂部[[德比郡足球俱乐部|德比郡]]外借至[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英超]]俱樂部[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]。

2002年，卡臣已經加盟了[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]的足球學院，並在2004年2月對[[曼聯足球會|曼聯]]的賽事中首次代表球會正選上場。同月，他亦首次代表[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格兰U21]]上陣。

2005年1月，卡臣以75萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]的身價轉投[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]，並於同年後期被徵召成為[[英格兰國家足球隊|英格兰國家隊]][[美國|美國]]夏季之旅的一員。他代表利物浦出賽9場，其中包括2005年4月對[[祖雲達斯足球會|祖雲達斯]]的[[歐洲聯賽冠軍盃|歐聯]]四強戰。其後，卡臣先後被球會租借給[[錫周三足球會|錫周三]]、[[查爾頓足球會|查爾頓]]和[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]以積累經驗。

参加完[[2007年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2007年歐洲U-21錦標]]後，卡臣在2007年11月對[[澳洲國家足球隊|澳洲]]的比賽中首次代表英格蘭出戰。2007/08球季，卡臣在阿士東維拉的借用期結束後返回利物浦，並於2008年7月以325萬英鎊加盟西布朗。

==球會生涯==
===列斯聯===
卡臣在[[坎布里亞郡|坎布里亞郡]]的{{Link-en|克利特穆爾|Cleator Moor}}長大，並就讀於當地的費因璽學校（Ehenside School）<ref name="Whitehaven News">{{Cite news |first=Alan |last=Irving |title=A new goal for Scott and Amy |url=http://www.whitehaven-news.co.uk/news/1.105815 |publisher=The Whitehaven News |date=2008-05-14 |accessdate=2008-08-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081012050500/http://www.whitehaven-news.co.uk/news/1.105815 |archivedate=2008-10-12 }}</ref>。卡臣年輕時，曾希望成為一位[[聯盟式橄欖球|聯盟式橄欖球]]球員<ref name="Carson glows in darkness">{{cite news|url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/sport/article-23379242-details/Carson+glows+in+darkness+of+Charlton+survival+bid/article.do|title=Carson glows in darkness of Charlton survival bid|date=22 December 2006|publisher=Evening Standard, The (London)|accessdate=2008-07-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081227034228/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/sport/article-23379242-details/Carson+glows+in+darkness+of+Charlton+survival+bid/article.do|archivedate=2008-12-27}}</ref>，但他最終決定專注於足球，並在十一二歲時成為校隊門將<ref name="Past Present Future">{{Cite news |title=PAST, PRESENT & FUTURE: Scott Carson |url=http://www.wba.co.uk/page/PastPresentandFuture/0,,10366~1371721,00.html |publisher=West Bromwich Albion F.C. |date=2008-08-21 |accessdate=2008-08-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090312004824/http://www.wba.co.uk/page/PastPresentandFuture/0%2C%2C10366~1371721%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-03-12 }}</ref>。他迅速由當地球隊{{le|克利特穆爾些路迪足球會|Cleator Moor Celtic F.C.|克利特穆爾些路迪}}的青年隊升入男子隊，儘管當時他只有15歲<ref name="Carson glows in darkness"/>。在為業餘球會[[沃京頓足球會|沃京頓]]出戰[[英格蘭足總青年杯|足總青年杯]]時，他的表現給前列斯聯後衛{{Link-en|彼得·咸頓|Peter Hampton}}留下深刻印象。最終，卡臣在2002年7月選擇加盟[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]的足球學院<ref name="Carson delight at U21 call-up">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/3177866.stm| title=Carson delight at U21 call-up|date=9 October 2003|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref>。他在學院待了不足一年的時間，又於預備組度過半季。2004年1月，在對[[米杜士堡足球會|米杜士堡]]的賽事中，由於門將[[保羅·羅賓遜_(1979年)|羅賓遜]]被罰出，他得以入替[[占士·米拿|占士·米拿]]，首次代表一隊登場<ref name="Soccerbase 03_04">{{cite web|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=35776&seasonid=133|title=Games played by Scott Carson in 2003/2004|work=Soccerbase|publisher=Racing Post|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref><ref name="Leeds 0-3 Middlesbrough">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/3417877.stm|title=Leeds 0-3 Middlesbrough|date=31 January 2004|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2004-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040419002950/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/3417877.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩週後，他在[[奧脫福球場|奧脫福球場]]對[[曼聯足球會|曼聯]]的賽事中首次正選上陣，雙方以1-1打平<ref name="Man Utd 1-1 Leeds">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/3496745.stm|title=Man Utd 1-1 Leeds|date=21 February 2004|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2004-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040619231944/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/3496745.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的第二次上陣則是在2004年5月對[[車路士足球會|車路士]]的賽事<ref name="Soccerbase 03_04" />。同月，羅賓遜離開了列斯聯，會方於兩個月後簽入[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]國門{{Link-en|尼爾·蘇利雲|Neil Sullivan}}，使卡臣需要與尼爾·蘇利雲競爭正選位置<ref name="Robinson seals Spurs move">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/3708683.stm|title=Robinson seals Spurs move|date=14 May 2004|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2004-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040722120333/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/3708683.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Sullivan joins Leeds">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/3939869.stm|title=Sullivan joins Leeds|date=31 July 2004|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref>，這則轉會亦促進了卡臣的提高<ref name="Carson can rely on Sullivan">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/3534484.stm|title=Carson can rely on Sullivan|date=4 August 2004|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref>。2004/05球季結束後，卡臣的合約亦到期，但列斯聯希望他留隊，因此在2004年12月向他提供了一份長期合約<ref name="Leeds to offer Carson fresh deal">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4079167.stm| title=Leeds to offer Carson fresh deal|date=8 December 2004|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref>。然而，卡臣最終選擇在2005年1月以75萬英鎊身價轉會至[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]<ref name="Carson seals switch to Liverpool ">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/4183677.stm|title=Carson seals switch to Liverpool|date=21 January 2005|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2007-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070902095107/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/4183677.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="West Brom snap up keeper Carson " />。

===利物浦===
卡臣與利物浦簽訂了為期四年半的合約，並與[[耶日·杜迪克|耶日·杜迪克]]競逐正選位置<ref name="Carson seals switch to Liverpool " />。2005年3月，他在對[[紐卡素足球會|紐卡素]]的賽事中首次代表利物浦正選上陣<ref name="Newcastle 1-0 Liverpool ">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/4300431.stm| title=Newcastle 1-0 Liverpool |date=5 March 2005|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref>，並在四月連續上陣三場，包括對[[祖雲達斯足球會|祖雲達斯]]的[[歐洲聯賽冠軍盃|歐聯]]四強賽事<ref name="Liverpool 2-1 Juventus ">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/4407891.stm|title=Liverpool 2-1 Juventus|date=5 April 2005|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2009-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090526045548/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/4407891.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Owls swoop for keeper Carson" />。雖然因利物浦贏得[[2005年歐洲聯賽冠軍盃決賽|2005年歐洲聯賽冠軍盃]]和[[2005年歐洲超級盃|2005年歐洲超級盃]]，卡臣亦獲得獎牌，但他沒有出現在其中任何一場比賽中<ref name="CL Final">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/4573159.stm|title=AC Milan 3-3 Liverpool (aet)|date=25 May 2005|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-10-06|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612150505/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/4573159.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Super Cup">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/4180288.stm|title=Liverpool 3-1 CSKA Moscow (aet)|date=26 August 2005|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-10-06|archive-date=2005-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051216145954/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/4180288.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。整個2005/06球季，他僅在四場杯賽中上陣<ref name="Soccerbase 04_05">{{cite web| url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=35776&seasonid=134| title=Games played by Scott Carson in 2004/2005|work=Soccerbase|publisher=Racing Post|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref><ref name="Soccerbase 05_06">{{cite web|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=35776&seasonid=134| title=Games played by Scott Carson in 2005/2006|work=Soccerbase|publisher=Racing Post|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref>。2006年3月，卡臣被外借至[[錫周三足球會|錫周三]]，他的加盟解決了錫周三缺乏門將的危機，他本人則希望有更多正選機會以爭取打入征戰[[2006年世界盃|2006年世界盃]]的英格蘭隊中<ref name="Owls swoop for keeper Carson">{{cite news|title=Owls swoop for keeper Carson|date=11 March 2006 |work=Football|publisher=Liverpool Echo}}</ref><ref name="Owls complete double loan swoop ">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_wed/4794486.stm|title=Owls complete double loan swoop|date=10 March 2006|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2007-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070903183427/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_wed/4794486.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Owls keeper's world cup bid owls">{{cite news|url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport1/Owls-keeper39s-world-cup-bid.1383040.jp|title=Owls keeper's world cup bid owls|date=11 March 2006|publisher=The Star (Sheffield)|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2009-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122102923/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport1/Owls-keeper39s-world-cup-bid.1383040.jp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡臣在錫周三上陣的9場賽事中，有5場未失球，當時的錫周三助教{{Link-en|奇雲·森馬菲特|Kevin Summerfield}}讚揚卡臣的貢獻是協助球隊擺脫降班危機的重要因素之一<ref name="Carson No 1 for Wednesday">{{cite news|url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport1/Loan-keeper-Carson-No-1.1474822.jp|title=Loan keeper Carson No 1 for Wednesday in Championship survival battle|date=1 May 2006|publisher=Star, The (Sheffield)|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2009-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122091325/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport1/Loan-keeper-Carson-No-1.1474822.jp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當季結束後，他重返利物浦，並於2006年7月續約至2011年<ref name="Carson sign new deal">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/5216254.stm|title=Carson & Anderson sign new deals|date=26 July 2006|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2007-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071006130048/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/5216254.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

僅僅到了2006年8月，因為[[查爾頓足球會|查爾頓]]收購[[諾域治足球會|諾域治]]門將[[羅拔·格連|羅拔·格連]]失敗後<ref name="Dowie's Plan B">{{cite news|title=Dowie's Plan B after Green's Hammer blow|last=Brooks|first=Gideon |date=15 August 2006 |publisher=Express, The (London)}}</ref>，卡臣便被利物浦外借至查爾頓<ref name="Carson signs for Charlton">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/4792167.stm|title=Carson signs for Charlton on loan|date=14 August 2006|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2006-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060825235049/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/4792167.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡臣對此解釋說：「利物浦希望我能積累一些經驗，然後希望我能在下季回來與[[荷西·連拿|荷西·連拿]]競逐正選位置。有數個[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會對我有興趣，但我需要在[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英超]]比賽，既然羅拔·格連、[[賓·科士打_(足球運動員)|賓·科士打]]和[[基斯·卻克蘭|基斯·卻克蘭]]不断表现自己，我也应该有所作为。<ref name="Carson hopes for Valley lift">{{cite news|first=Wayne |last=Veysey |title=Carson hopes for Valley lift|date=18 August 2006 |publisher=Evening Standard, The (London)}}</ref>」在38場英超賽事中，他總共上陣36場，僅因借用合約的條款規定而缺席了兩場對利物浦的比賽<ref name="Charlton sunk by Reds">{{cite news |first=Gary |last=Haines |url=http://www.charlton-athletic.co.uk/newsview.ink?matchid=4104&type=m |title=Charlton sunk by Reds |date=2006-12-16 |publisher=Charlton Athletic F.C. |accessdate=2008-08-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081227034241/http://www.charlton-athletic.co.uk/newsview.ink?matchid=4104&type=m |archivedate=2008-12-27 }}</ref><ref name="Addicks bow out with a bang">{{cite news |first=Gary |last=Haines |url=http://www.charlton-athletic.co.uk/newsview.ink?matchid=4105&type=m |title=Addicks bow out with a bang |date=2007-05-13 |publisher=Charlton Athletic F.C. |accessdate=2008-08-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081227034246/http://www.charlton-athletic.co.uk/newsview.ink?matchid=4105&type=m |archivedate=2008-12-27 }}</ref>。2006/07球季結束後，卡臣雖然未能挽回查爾頓降班的命運<ref name="Liverpool include Carson in plans" />，他的凸出表現仍使他獲得查爾頓支持者年度最佳球員，且成為首位獲得殊榮的借用球員<ref name="Carson picks up award">{{cite news|first=Lindsay|last=McCombie|url=http://www.charlton-athletic.co.uk/newsview.ink?nid=30798&newstype=p|title=Carson keeping faith|date=30 April 2007|publisher=Charlton Athletic F.C.|accessdate=2008-09-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081227034252/http://www.charlton-athletic.co.uk/newsview.ink?nid=30798&newstype=p|archivedate=2008-12-27}}</ref><ref name="Fans' choice Carson drops clanger ">{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-5894379.html|title=Fans' choice Carson drops clanger |date=30 April 2007 |publisher=Evening Standard, The (London)|accessdate=2008-09-04}}{{dead link|date=July 2015}}</ref>。

2007/08球季，卡臣回到利物浦，並在2007年6月被領隊[[拉法埃爾·賓尼迪斯|拉法埃爾·賓尼迪斯]]確定為一隊成員，拉法埃爾·賓尼迪斯說：「於現在起，他必須與荷西·連拿競爭正選位置。<ref name="Liverpool include Carson in plans">{{cite news |title=Liverpool include Carson in plans |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/6231308.stm |publisher=BBC Sport |date=22 July 2007 |accessdate=2007-06-22 |archive-date=2007-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070812073742/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/6231308.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>」其後，卡臣擔當球隊的第二門將。但利物浦於2007年8月簽入[[查理斯·伊坦積|查理斯·伊坦積]]後，卡臣面臨進一步的競爭。最終，卡臣再次被外借，這次是[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]，阿士東維拉因此付出200萬英鎊。拉法埃爾·賓尼迪斯談到這次交易時說：「我們並不想出售他，我們與他的合作非常愉快。但是他需要比賽以保住他在英格蘭隊的位置。<ref name="Villa close in on keeper Carson ">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/6938522.stm|title=Villa close in on keeper Carson|date=9 August 2007|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2021-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210704025403/https://secure-uk.imrworldwide.com/v51.js|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Villa sign keeper Carson on loan ">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/6941147.stm|title=Villa sign keeper Carson on loan|date=10 August 2007|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2008-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080204053930/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/6941147.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>」阿士東維拉領隊[[馬田·奧尼爾|馬田·奧尼爾]]重用卡臣，多於[[湯馬士·蘇連遜|湯馬士·蘇連遜]]和[[史超活·泰萊|史超活·泰萊]]，卡臣最終在38場聯賽賽事中上陣36場，其中沒有上陣的兩場仍然是對利物浦<ref name="Villa sign keeper Carson on loan " /><ref name="Martin O’Neill says ">{{cite news| url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/aston_villa/article3221986.ece |title=Martin O’Neill says US owner is with Villa for long haul|last=Lansley|first=Peter |date=21 January 2008|publisher=Times, The (London)|accessdate=2008-09-07}}</ref>，且在2007/08球季保持11場不失球<ref name="Villa can keep Carson - Benitez">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/7096859.stm|title=Villa can keep Carson - Benitez|date=15 November 2007|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2007-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071118155053/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/7096859.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Soccerbase 07_08">{{cite web| url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=35776&seasonid=137|title=Games played by Scott Carson in 2007/2008|work=Soccerbase|publisher=Racing Post|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref>。在對[[曼聯足球會|曼聯]]的賽事中，他因侵犯對方球員[[卡路士·泰維斯|卡路士·泰維斯]]而首次領到紅牌<ref name="red card">{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7043000.stm|title=Aston Villa 1-4 Man Utd|publisher=BBC Sport|date=20 October 2007|accessdate=2008-09-24|archive-date=2009-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501215346/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7043000.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===西布朗===
2007/08球季結束後，卡臣重返利物浦。2008年7月，他以325萬英鎊加盟[[西布朗足球會|西布朗]]，簽訂了四年合約並隨著會方附加的續約條款而增加至375萬英鎊<ref name="West Brom snap up keeper Carson ">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7514218.stm| title=West Brom snap up keeper Carson |date=18 July 2008|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-18}}</ref>。自2004年在列斯聯首次上陣後，卡臣已加盟過五家球會，他表明希望在一間球會安頓下來，並說：「我在這三、四年間就像一個流浪漢。植根和安頓下來將會是很好的選擇。我可以預期，會在這裡待四、五年甚至更長。<ref name="Carson wants lengthy Baggies stay ">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/7525301.stm |title=Carson wants lengthy Baggies stay |date=25 July 2008|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-09-04}}</ref>」[[2008年至2009年英格蘭超級聯賽|2008/09球季]]，卡臣在開幕戰對[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]的賽事中首次代表西布朗上陣，最終球會以0-1不敵對手<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.wba.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10366~43689,00.html |title=Arsenal vs WBA |date=2008-08-16 |publisher=West Bromwich Albion F.C. |accessdate=2008-08-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919095830/http://www.wba.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0%2C%2C10366~43689%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-09-19 }}</ref>。

2011年1月13日，在接連犯錯導致球隊落敗後，時任領隊[[罗伯托·迪马特奥|罗伯托·迪马特奥]]決定更換門將，由夏季加盟的[[博阿兹·米希尔|博阿兹·米希尔]]代替卡臣上陣，而他亦同時失去[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]臂章<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/9361061.stm |title=Di Matteo drops West Brom keeper Carson for errors |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-13 |accessdate=2011-01-18 |archive-date=2011-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110117111841/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/9361061.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===貝沙===
2011年7月1日卡臣與[[土超|土超]]球會[[布尔萨体育|貝沙]]達成私人條件後正式動筆加盟，轉會費沒有透露<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13906698.stm |title=West Bromwich Albion's Scott Carson joins Bursaspor |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-01 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2011-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110702112334/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13906698.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===韋根===
2013年7月4日，離開英格蘭球壇兩年的卡臣由[[土超|土超]]球會[[布尔萨体育|貝沙]]轉投[[英冠|英冠]]球會韋根，轉會費金額沒有透露，合約為期三年<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23168976 |title=Scott Carson: Wigan Athletic sign Bursaspor goalkeeper |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-07-04 |accessdate=2013-11-18 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017021043/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23168976 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===曼城===
2019年8月8日，卡森由德比郡租借至曼城，租期2019-20賽季，成為僅次於[[艾達臣·摩拉斯|埃德森]]和[[克勞迪歐·布拉沃|克勞迪歐·布拉沃]]的第三門將。他將租借延長至2020-21賽季
<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mancity.com/news/mens/scott-carson-loan-transfer-news-63733459 |title=CARSON EXTENDS CITY STAY |accessdate=2020-08-28 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829195002/https://www.mancity.com/news/mens/scott-carson-loan-transfer-news-63733459 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 國際賽生涯 ==
2003年10月，卡臣首次獲選進入[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格兰U21]]，參加對[[土耳其21歲以下國家足球隊|土耳其U21]]的[[2007年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2007年歐洲U-21錦標]]的資格賽。當時，他還未競爭到列斯聯一隊的位置<ref name="Carson delight at U21 call-up" />，在此之前，他只在英格蘭其他級別出場過四次。2004年2月，他參加了對[[荷蘭21歲以下國家足球隊|荷蘭U21]]的比賽，英格蘭隊最終以3-2勝出<ref name="England U21 3-2 Holland U21">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/3493515.stm |title=England U21 3-2 Holland U21 |date=17 February 2004|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20}}</ref>。此後，卡臣進入2007年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽的英軍名單，並在第三場對[[塞爾維亞21歲以下國家足球隊|塞爾維亞U21]]時上陣，第28次出戰U21賽事<ref name="England U21 2-0 Serbia U21">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6759921.stm|title=England U21 2-0 Serbia U21|date=2007-06-17|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-08-05|archive-date=2007-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071007020918/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6759921.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ugly atmosphere mars battling England win">{{cite news|title=Ugly atmosphere mars battling England win|last=McGrath|first=Mike|date=18 June 2007|publisher=Birmingham Post}}</ref>，打破了由[[加雷斯·巴里|加雷斯·巴里]]和[[占美·加歷查|占美·加歷查]]所保持的紀錄<ref name="Liverpool goalkeeper Scott Carson">{{cite news|title=Liverpool goalkeeper Scott Carson will ...|date=17 June 2007|publisher=Express on Sunday, The (London)}}</ref>。他的第29場也是最後一場U21賽事是對荷蘭的八強戰，加時後，雙方1-1平手，只得以[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]一決勝負。雖然卡臣在16個[[點球|點球]]中撲到一球，自己也射入了一球，英格蘭隊最終仍以12-13輸給對手<ref name="Holland U21 1-1 Eng U21 (aet)">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6766603.stm|title=Holland U21 1-1 Eng U21 (aet)|date=2007-06-20|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-08-05|archive-date=2009-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130044524/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6766603.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡臣成為英格蘭U21上陣次數最多紀錄的保持者，後來才被[[占士·米拿|占士·米拿]]所取代<ref name="Montenegro U21 0-3 England U21">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6984539.stm|title=Montenegro U21 0-3 England U21|date=7 September 2008|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-08-06|archive-date=2021-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210904110801/https://secure-uk.imrworldwide.com/cgi-bin/m?rnd=1630753681101&ci=bbc&cg=0&sr=1600x1000&ts=v51.js&cd=24&lg=en-US&je=n&ck=y&tz=0&ct=&hp=&tl=BBC%20SPORT%20%7C%20Football%20%7C%20Internationals%20%7C%20Montenegro%20U21%200-3%20England%20U21&si=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport2%2Fhi%2Ffootball%2Finternationals%2F6984539.stm&rp=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2005年5月，尚為英格蘭U21一員的卡臣受到[[英格蘭國家足球隊|英格蘭]]徵召，加入英格蘭[[美國|美國]]夏季之旅<ref name="Crouch nets England squad call-up">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/4518717.stm| title=Crouch nets England squad call-up|date=12 May 2005|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-08-06}}</ref>。一年後的2006年5月，卡臣在對[[白俄羅斯國家足球隊|白俄羅斯]]的國際友誼賽中替補受傷的[[羅拔·格連|羅拔·格連]]，首次代表[[英格蘭足球代表乙隊|英格蘭B隊]]出場<ref name="England B 1-2 Belarus ">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/teams/england/5017924.stm|title=England B 1-2 Belarus|date=26 May 2006|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-08-09|archive-date=2009-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501191058/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/teams/england/5017924.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於羅拔·格連亦是[[2006年世界盃|2006年世界盃]]英格蘭隊的成員，他的受傷給卡臣帶來了機會。<ref name="Carson promoted to England squad">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/teams/england/5020060.stm|title=Carson promoted to England squad|date=26 May 2006|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2006-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061214164034/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/teams/england/5020060.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管卡臣還從未有代表英格蘭隊的經歷，他最終仍然如願獲選<ref name="McClaren plays it safe with squad">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6453061.stm|title=McClaren plays it safe with squad|date=16 March 2007|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-08-09|archive-date=2007-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070329104047/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6453061.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Beckham recalled to England squad ">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6694743.stm|title=Beckham recalled to England squad|date=26 May 2007|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-08-09|archive-date=2007-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071005195058/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6694743.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於2007年5月在對[[阿爾巴尼亞國家足球隊|阿爾巴尼亞]]的賽事中第二次代表英格蘭B隊上陣，球隊以3-1的比分擊敗對手<ref name="England B 3-1 Albania ">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6670865.stm|title=England B 3-1 Albania|date=26 May 2007|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-08-09|archive-date=2012-09-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6APKZG1kV?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6670865.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年的歐洲U-21足球錦標賽後，卡臣在11月對[[澳洲國家足球隊|澳洲]]的友誼賽中首次代表英格蘭上陣<ref name="Carson's debut delight">{{cite news|first=Stuart|last=Mawhinney|url=http://www.thefa.com/England/SeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2007/11/AusEng_CarsonReaction.htm|title=Carson's debut delight|date=11 November 2007|publisher=The Football Association|accessdate=2008-08-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20071029052642/http://www.thefa.com/England/SeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2007/11/AusEng_CarsonReaction.htm|archivedate=2007-10-29}}</ref>。一週後，他又在[[2008年歐洲國家盃|2008年歐洲國家盃]]對[[克羅地亞國家足球隊|克羅地亞]]的關鍵比賽中上陣，英格蘭隊卻最終以2-3落敗而被淘汰。卡臣被認為需要對第一個失球負責，他未能預測到[[尼高·卡蘭積卡|尼高·卡蘭積卡]]30碼外射門的下墜軌跡，球在他面前彈起，結果他只能將球擋入球門內<ref name="England 2-3 Croatia ">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7103110.stm |title=England 2-3 Croatia |last=Stevenson |first=Jonathan |date=21 November 2007 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=2008-09-04 |archive-date=2007-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071122091808/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7103110.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Carson calamity">{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/internationals/england-2-croatia-3-carson-calamity-sets-the-tone-as-abject-england-reach-alltime-low-759050.html |title=England 2 Croatia 3: Carson calamity sets the tone as abject England reach all-time low |last=Wallace |first=Sam |date=22 November 2007 |publisher=Independent, The (London) |accessdate=2008-08-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201151609/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/internationals/england-2-croatia-3-carson-calamity-sets-the-tone-as-abject-england-reach-alltime-low-759050.html |archivedate=2008-12-01 }}</ref>。翌日，時任英格蘭領隊[[史提夫·麥卡倫|史提夫·麥卡倫]]被解僱<ref name="Steve McClaren is sacked">{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/internationals/steve-mcclaren-is-sacked-759045.html |title=Steve McClaren is sacked |date=22 November 2007 |publisher=Independent, The (London) |accessdate=2008-08-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201150834/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/internationals/steve-mcclaren-is-sacked-759045.html |archivedate=2008-12-01 }}</ref>，體育評論員批評史提夫·麥卡倫在這場比賽選擇了一個毫無經驗的門將<ref name="England in gutter">{{cite news|title=Rain over - England 2 Croatia 3: We're in the gutter|last=Whittingham|first=Stewart |date=22 November 2007 |publisher=Sun, The (London)|page=2}}</ref><ref name="Don't blame Carson">{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2007/nov/25/newsstory.sport7|title=Don't blame Carson - the real gaffe was exposing him to such high pressure|last=James|first=David|date=25 November 2007|publisher=Observer, The (London)|accessdate=2008-08-09|archive-date=2009-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090322034151/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2007/nov/25/newsstory.sport7|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

新任領隊[[法比奧·卡比路|法比奧·卡比路]]將卡臣選進英格蘭隊在2008年2月對[[瑞士國家足球隊|瑞士]]友誼賽的名單中<ref name="Capello keeps Agbonlahor in squad">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7224293.stm|title=Capello keeps Agbonlahor in squad|date=2 February 2008|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-08-09|archive-date=2008-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080206144504/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7224293.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一個月後，他因傷而沒有獲選出戰[[法國國家足球隊|法國]]的賽事<ref name="Lampard & Rooney fit for England">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7309440.stm|title=Beckham recalled to England squad|date=24 March 2008|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-10-06|archive-date=2008-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080329062924/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7309440.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡臣在五場國際賽均未被徵召後，終於在2008年10月獲重新徵召入對[[哈薩克國家足球隊|哈薩克]]和[[白俄羅斯國家足球隊|白俄羅斯]]的[[2010年世界盃外圍賽_(歐洲區)|2010年世界盃外圍賽賽事]]的名單中<ref name="Scott Carson earns England recall">{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghampost.net/midlands-birmingham-sport/west-midlands-sports/west-bromwich-albion-fc/2008/10/06/scott-carson-earns-england-recall-65233-21973668/ |title=Scott Carson earns England recall |date=6 October 2008 |publisher=Birmingham Post |accessdate=2008-10-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081009020325/http://www.birminghampost.net/midlands-birmingham-sport/west-midlands-sports/west-bromwich-albion-fc/2008/10/06/scott-carson-earns-england-recall-65233-21973668/ |archivedate=2008-10-09 }}</ref><ref name="England matches played">{{cite news |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/SeniorTeam/Archive/default.htm?i=2&pf=t&searchname=england&ap=c&t=m |title=England: matches played |publisher=FA |accessdate=2008-10-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080912100340/http://www.thefa.com/England/SeniorTeam/Archive/default.htm?i=2&amp%3Bpf=t&amp%3Bsearchname=england&amp%3Bap=c&amp%3Bt=m |archivedate=2008-09-12 }}</ref>。2008年11月，卡臣在[[柏林|柏林]]對[[德國國家足球隊|德國]]的賽事中後備入替，這是他第三次代表英格蘭隊上陣，亦使他成為近24年來，首位代表英格蘭隊上陣的西布朗球員<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.wba.premiumtv.co.uk/page/News/0,,10366~1459989,00.html |title=Carson earns England cap |publisher=West Bromwich Albion F.C. |date=19 November 2008 |accessdate=2008-11-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081227034435/http://www.wba.premiumtv.co.uk/page/News/0%2C%2C10366~1459989%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-12-27 }}</ref>。

==個人生活==

2008年5月17日，卡臣與艾美·巴頓（Amy Barton）在{{Link-en|埃格雷蒙特|Egremont}}結婚，並育有一子希頓（Hayden）<ref name="Whitehaven News"/><ref name="Past Present Future"/> 。卡臣的弟弟格蘭（Grant）亦是一名門將，曾效力[[卡素爾聯足球會|卡素爾]]<ref>{{Cite news
